    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nThe following errors have been generated by trying to comment lines on nonmodifiable buffers (e.g. help, health) using the built-in mapping \"gcc\"\n\n```\nOption 'commentstring' is empty.\nE5108: Error executing lua /usr/local/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/_comment.lua:210: Buffer is not 'modifiable'\nstack traceback:\n        [C]: in function '_with'\n        /usr/local/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/_comment.lua:209: in function 'toggle_lines'\n        /usr/local/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/_comment.lua:240: in function </usr/local/share/nvim/runtime/lua/vim/_comment.lua:219>\n```\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nInfo message or warning.",
