    "comment_data": [
        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Throwing error is consistent with how other built-in operators (like `d`, `gu`, etc.) behave: they show `E21: Cannot make changes, 'modifiable' is off` error. The difference is only in the amount of text shown: `gc` has more of it as it is implemented in Lua, which can't be helped much.\n\nAs having behavior which is consistent (at least in the exception level) across all built-in operators is a good thing, I think it is better to close this.",
